sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Workstation<br/>(kubectl rhaii-validate all)
    participant API as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Controller<br/>(orchestrator)
    participant CRD as CRD API<br/>(apiextensions.k8s.io)
    participant GPUJob as GPU Check Job<br/>(privileged pod)
    participant NvidiaSMI as nvidia-smi<br/>(host process)
    participant Sysfs as /sys/bus/pci<br/>(host filesystem)
    participant IperfSrv as iperf3 Server<br/>5201/TCP
    participant IperfCli as iperf3 Client
    participant RDMASrv as ib_write_bw Server<br/>18515/TCP RDMA
    participant RDMACli as ib_write_bw Client
    participant PingSrv as ibv_rc_pingpong Server<br/>dynamic/TCP RDMA RC
    participant PingCli as ibv_rc_pingpong Client
    participant CM as ConfigMap<br/>(report storage)

    Note over User,CM: Phase 1: Dependency Checks (no cluster resources created)
    User->>API: kubectl rhaii-validate all<br/>Auth: kubeconfig credentials
    API->>Controller: Initialize validation
    Controller->>CRD: GET CRDs (Gateway API, InferencePool, LWS, cert-manager)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    CRD-->>Controller: CRD presence results
    Controller->>API: LIST pods in cert-manager, istio-system, openshift-lws-operator<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    API-->>Controller: Operator health status

    Note over User,CM: Phase 2: Per-Node GPU & RDMA Checks
    Controller->>API: CREATE namespace, RBAC, Jobs (per GPU node)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    API->>GPUJob: Deploy privileged Job (hostPID, host volumes)
    GPUJob->>NvidiaSMI: exec nvidia-smi<br/>(privileged container)
    NvidiaSMI-->>GPUJob: Driver version, ECC status, GPU info
    GPUJob->>Sysfs: Read /sys/bus/pci, /sys/class/infiniband<br/>(host volume mount)
    Sysfs-->>GPUJob: NUMA topology, PCIe hierarchy, RDMA devices
    GPUJob-->>Controller: Results via pod logs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,CM: Phase 3: TCP Bandwidth Tests
    Controller->>IperfSrv: Deploy iperf3 server Job (tools image)
    Controller->>IperfCli: Deploy iperf3 client Job (tools image)
    IperfCli->>IperfSrv: TCP bandwidth test<br/>5201/TCP, No encryption
    IperfSrv-->>IperfCli: Bandwidth results
    IperfCli-->>Controller: Results via pod logs

    Note over User,CM: Phase 4: RDMA Bandwidth Tests
    Controller->>RDMASrv: Deploy ib_write_bw server Job (tools image + CUDA)
    Controller->>RDMACli: Deploy ib_write_bw client Job (tools image + CUDA)
    RDMACli->>RDMASrv: RDMA write bandwidth (GPUDirect)<br/>18515+/TCP, RDMA verbs, No encryption
    RDMASrv-->>RDMACli: Bandwidth results
    RDMACli-->>Controller: Results via pod logs

    Note over User,CM: Phase 5: RDMA Connectivity Mesh (Pingmesh)
    Controller->>CM: Read topology from stored report<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Controller->>PingSrv: Deploy ibv_rc_pingpong servers (N-choose-2 pairs)
    Controller->>PingCli: Deploy ibv_rc_pingpong clients
    PingCli->>PingSrv: RDMA RC transport test<br/>dynamic/TCP, No encryption
    PingSrv-->>PingCli: Connectivity result
    PingCli-->>Controller: Results via pod logs

    Note over User,CM: Phase 6: Report Generation
    Controller->>CM: Store results in rhaii-validate-report ConfigMap<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, ServiceAccount token
    Controller-->>User: Print results (table or JSON)
